the assertion assumes that only certain types of nodes can be children of
gather nodes with `EdgeIdx == UINT_MAX`. However, in this reproducer, we have a
gather pattern where a PHI node bundle references multiple different load
instructions, creating a tree entry that doesn't meet any of the expected
conditions. The PHI nodes are creating a complex dependency structure that
results in a non-splat, non-extractelement node being processed in this
context, which violates the assertion's assumptions.\n\n4. **Proposed Edit
